description: Variation of Condition 1 (approved plans) of planning permission dated 12 August 2013 (RN: 09/09773)  for the demolition of the existing structures and development of buildings between 5 and 12 storeys comprising 131 private and affordable flats, ancillary leisure and gym facility, 103 car parking spaces and 258 cycle spaces; Namely to allow amendments to the approved scheme including alterations to the depth of the basement and height of the ground floor, reduction in number of flats from 131 to 128 and change of 1 x 1 bed flat to studio flat at ground floor level,  alterations to the front entrance ramp, changes to external appearance of the building, lowering of the third floor terrace; installation of car stacker system to basement, changes to internal layout, updated energy strategy and other and associated alterations.
